rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0002
rows.name: There's plenty, so please eat as much as you want![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0005
rows.name: Smells good. Gwin, don't eat too much.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0006
rows.name: I don't want to hear that from you, Lieutenant.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0007
rows.name: This is what the ancient saying calls "eating from the same pot."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0008
rows.name:
I wondered what was going on...
We have a battle coming up, you know![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0009
rows.name:
That's exactly why!
They say you can't fight on an empty stomach, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0010
rows.name:
The Central Life's operating time is running out.
If it hits zero, everything ends.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0011
rows.name: Besides, the enemy might already be inside the Central Life.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0014
rows.name: The fate of humanity rests on this battle.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0015
rows.name: Why are you getting so heated, Doug? Nagi said it too.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0016
rows.name: The coordinate analysis for the Central Life takes two hours.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0017
rows.name: I know that! But that doesn't mean we should be this leisurely[ST:wide ]—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0018
rows.name: You really don't get it at all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0020
rows.name: It's not just you. Everyone is anxious. Everyone is uneasy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0024
rows.name: Lin, in her own way, was trying to ease everyone's anxiety.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0025
rows.name: If you trouble Lin-san, Tatsu will get angry-meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0027
rows.name: Lin, sorry for snapping at you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0028
rows.name: It's as Irina says. I was definitely feeling anxious and uneasy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0030
rows.name: I won't forgive you! The penalty is ten cups of special cocoa![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0031
rows.name: From that shop, right? Okay, roger that![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_SEL0021
rows.name: Reach for the food without looking aside.

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0032
rows.name: Now, let's all eat Lin's home cooking.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0043
rows.name: Lin, it was delicious. Thank you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0044
rows.name:
It was my first time eating it,
but I understand why Commander Vandham and Irina come to eat so often.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0047
rows.name: Being praised to my face like that makes me shy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0048
rows.name: Well then, I should head back soon. Thanks for the food.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0050
rows.name: Yeah, right. Lin, it was fun.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0052
rows.name: Well then, I shall take my leave. It was a fun festival.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12020100_MSG0054
rows.name:
Elma, the coordinate analysis is finished.
Come immediately with your team members.[ST:wait ]
